ZH: 我们一家五口坐轿车去旅行。
EN: The five of us took a sedan for a trip.

ZH: 昨天我朋友开他的轿车带我去超市。
EN: Yesterday my friend drove his sedan to take me to the supermarket.

ZH: 这辆轿车的油耗很高。
EN: This sedan has high fuel consumption.

ZH: 我的轿车是黑色的。
EN: My sedan is black in color.

ZH: 这个车库里停着很多轿车。
EN: There are many sedans parked in the garage.

ZH: 这辆轿车的发动机很强劲。
EN: The engine of this sedan is very powerful.

ZH: 买一辆轿车需要花费很多钱。
EN: Buying a sedan costs a lot of money.

ZH: 我们租了一辆轿车去迎接客人。
EN: We rented a sedan to pick up the guests.

ZH: 警察用轿车在城市巡逻。
EN: Police patrol the city using sedans.

ZH: 家里的轿车需要进行定期保养。
EN: The sedan at home needs regular maintenance.

ZH: 高速路上轿车行驶的速度很快。
EN: Sedans travel at high speeds on the highway.

ZH: 这辆轿车的外观设计很时尚。
EN: The exterior design of this sedan is very fashionable.

ZH: 要小心驾驶轿车，不要超速。
EN: Drive the sedan carefully and do not speed.

ZH: 老板每天都开轿车去上班。
EN: The boss drives to work in a sedan every day.

ZH: 她的新轿车是她的生日礼物。
EN: Her new sedan is a birthday gift.

ZH: 这辆轿车的座位很宽敞舒适。
EN: The seats of this sedan are spacious and comfortable.

ZH: 我想换一辆更环保的轿车。
EN: I want to switch to a more environmentally friendly sedan.

ZH: 这辆轿车很节能，也很省钱。
EN: This sedan is energy-efficient and economical.

ZH: 轿车是我出差时最方便的交通工具。
EN: Sedans are the most convenient means of transportation when I travel for work.

ZH: 这款轿车有四扇门，很适合家庭使用。
EN: This sedan has four doors, perfect for family use.
